<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-15151] Cannot use placeholders on RedeliveryPolicy enums</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-15151</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;redeliveryPolicy retryAttemptedLogLevel=&quot;{{&lt;tt&gt;placeholder&lt;/tt&gt;}}&quot;/&amp;gt; does not work due to IllegalArgumentException: no enum constant org.apache.camel.LoggingLevel.{{&lt;tt&gt;placeholder&lt;/tt&gt;}}.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
